## Installation
```bash
yarn add @cresteem/richie-js

or

npm i @cresteem/richie-js
```

## 👨🏻‍💻 CLI

```bash
hawk -s indexnow

or

hawk -s gindex

or

hawk -s gwebmaster

or

hawk -s gwebmaster2
```

[learn more about Hawk JS](https://www.cresteem.com/opensource/hawk-js)

